INSERT INTO `products` (`id`, `title`, `url`, `meta_title`, `meta_description`, `additional_code`, `main_image`, `related_products`, `brand`, `status`, `long_description`, `applications`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(58, 'Precipitated Silica', 'silica', 'Leading Precipitated Silica Manufacturer & Supplier in India', 'MLA Group is a leading Indian manufacturers & suppliers of Precipitated Silica, we are one of the best exporter of Silica in the whole world at best price.', 'Test', 'product-image/precipitated-silica-386705336-vhedh.webp', '', '22', 'Unpublished', '<h3>EXCELLENCE THROUGH RESEARCH &amp; DEVLOPMENT</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Synthetic Silica Products and Kanpur Chemical Industries, units of MLA Group of Industries are one of the largest manufacturers of precipitated silica / hydrated silica / amorphous silica / silicic acid and silicates today, having complete vertical integration, rigid quality control standards and unique product properties. Not only have we stood the competition against multinationals, but are the leaders in several fronts, where through intensive research we have developed products with unmatched properties, by standards. We cater to every segment of the market with user specific products. We started operations in 1985 and have today grown into a company with an annual production of 4000 MT/Annum and an expediture as high as 10% of net profits on R &amp; D annually.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are the leading manufacturer of precipitated calcium silicates in India and have promising quality over our products. We ensure multiple testing of our products through the experts and professionals which helped us to stand as leading precipitated silica suppliers/exporters in the world, following are some of ours unique properties:</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>A. VERY HIGH WATER / OIL ABSORPTION</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Upto 600% has been achieved and efforts are in progress to achieve the 800% mark. Most competing products have water-absorption upto 300% maximum only.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>B. VERY LOW BULK DENSITIES</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Upto 0.04 gm/cc has been achieved whereas competing products have 0.12 gm/cc minimum.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>C. VERY HIGH SURFACE AREAS</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Upto 600 m2/gm has been achieved.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>PRODUCTION FACILITIES</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Precipitation is carried out in microprocessor controlled batch reaction vessels, followed by filler-presses/vaccum filters and flash/spray driers and finally micro-mill with classifier for micronization wherever required.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>PESTICIDES</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/images/pesticides-one.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;For improvement in the suspension power and as a carrier for the active igredients, specially malathion, acephate and isoproton based formulations.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;For improvement of free-flow characteristics and storage stability.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;As a grinding auxillary.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>FEEDSTUFFS &amp; FOOD ITEMS</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/images/fooditems.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Improvement in free-flow properties and storage stability of table salt, spices etc.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Anticaking of milk extenders and fat concentrates, feedstuff urea &amp; mineral mixtures.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Conversion of 75% acqueous choline chloride solution into stable 50% powder form.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Conversion of liquid active substances into powder form, e.g. ethoxyquin, flavours &amp; fragrances.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>CHEMICALS - PRECIPITATED SILICA</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/images/chemical.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Conversion of liquids to free flowing powder form (e.g. SP antioxidant &amp; other rubber chemicals).</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;As a grinding aid (e.g. with sulphur).</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;For anti-caking &amp; free flow. (e.g. Detergents).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>PLASTICS &amp; POLYMERS - PRECIPITATED SILICA</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/images/shoes.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;To provide reinforcement properties in PP, PVC, PE and Polystyrene based master batches.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;As an anti-blocking agent in blown films &amp; foils.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Improvement in the mechanical characterstics of PVC flooring.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;With Phenol + melamine resins for anti-caking during storage and improvement in dosing properties of molding compounds.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Auxillary during production of polychloroprene based adhesives.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;With thermoplastic rubber for reduction in abrasion and increase in dimensional heat stability.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Reinforcement of Natural, SBR, Silicone, EVA, Nitrile, EPDM &amp; other rubbers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>OTHER PRODUCTS</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Liquid Systems</strong><br />\r\n	Due to high surface area they function as clarifying and adsorption agents (e.g.beverages).</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Adhesives</strong><br />\r\n	To adjust rheology and provide reinforcement.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Greases / Lubricants</strong><br />\r\n	For rheology control.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Paint, Dyes &amp; Printing inks</strong><br />\r\n	As a flatting / matting agent to reduce gloss or as a filler.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Paper Industry</strong><br />\r\n	Provides lightness, whiteness &amp; improves mechanical properties.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Toothpaste &amp; Polishes</strong><br />\r\n	As a mild abrasive and for rheology control.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Pharmaceuticals</strong><br />\r\n	As a processing aid in tabletting &amp; pelletizing.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cosmetics</strong><br />\r\n	For rheology control.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>UNISIL PRECIPITATED SILICA</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>UNISIL precipitated Silicas are available in various combinations of physical properties such primary and secondary particle size, surface area, bulk density, absorption capacity etc. It is available in three physical form Categories:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Powder Products</li>\r\n	<li>Spray Dried Granules</li>\r\n	<li>Compacted Pellets</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h2>FAQ&#39;S</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>WHY SHOULD I PURCHASE PRECIPITATED SILICA FROM THE MLA GROUP?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group, we fabricate items under a controlled climate and with high accuracy, severe quality controls, and standardized systems to present to you the best item each and every time. Because of our colossal limit and methodology, our costs are generally economical. We are the Leading Precipitated Silica manufacturers in India who are focused on constant improvement through R&amp;D, to serve the clients with quality items at lower costs through higher usefulness and unparalleled client service.</p>\r\n', '<h3>UNISIL NK precipitated silicas having high absorption capacities can be used to provide one or several of the following properties:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Free - flow</li>\r\n	<li>Thixotropy</li>\r\n	<li>Carrying Agent</li>\r\n	<li>Anticaking</li>\r\n	<li>Flatting</li>\r\n	<li>Matting</li>\r\n	<li>Reinforcement</li>\r\n	<li>Insulation</li>\r\n	<li>Lightness</li>\r\n	<li>Rheology Control</li>\r\n	<li>Suspension</li>\r\n	<li>Inert filler</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2024-04-25 07:21:09', '2024-06-30 10:25:42'),
(59, 'PVC Heat Stabilizers', 'pvc-heat-stabilizers', 'Leading PVC heat stabilizers manufacturers & supplier India', 'Buy PVC heat stabilizers from leading world-class manufactures at the most affordable rates, we are a certified suppliers & exporter of stabilizers in India.', 'text', 'product-image/25kg-pvc-heat-stabilizer-uniflow-500x500.webp', '\"9\"', '16', 'Published', '<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/silica.html\">Precipitated Silica</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/aluminium.html\">Aluminium Silicate</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/talc.html\">Micronized Talc/Barytes</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/zinc.html\">Zinc Oxide (Active / Transparent)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/silicate.html\">Hydrated Calcium Silicate</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/download/aluminium%20stearate%20hi-gel.doc\">Aluminium Stearate</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/download/UNIMUL.doc\">Glycerol Mono Stearate (GMS)</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/clays.html\">Levigated / Micronized China clays</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/dolomite.html\">Micronized Calcite / Dolomite</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/zincstearate.html\">Zinc Stearate / Calcium Stearate</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/calciumsulphate.html\">Calcium Sulphate</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/download/ADC-Blowing_agents.doc\">Azodicarbonamide (ADC) Blowing Agent</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/download/ONE_PACK_PVC_PP_.doc\">PVC stabilizers - Powder form ( UNISTAB - PP series )</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/download/ONE_PACK_PVC_LPF_.doc\">PVC stabilizers - Flakes form ( UNISTAB - LPF series)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/download/UNIZINC-%20white%20seal.doc\">Zinc oxide ( white seal - 99.5 % and pharma grade )</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>PVC HEAT STABILIZERS</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group Of Industries is a&nbsp;<strong>leading PVC heat stabilizer manufacturers in India</strong>, involved in the production of PVC heat stabilizers of premium quality.Starting from a single reactor the company now has grown multi-fold to be the leading PVC Stabilizer manufacturer in India. The company has a production capacity of 3000 tons per month. One of the key players in the PVC additives industry, we have been the preferred&nbsp;<strong>PVC heat stabilizer suppliers in the world</strong>, supplying high performance stabilizers to a large number of PVC manufacturing companies across the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are committed to providing our customers best quality products at competitive prices. With fast and reliable supplies, we have grown into the most reliable brand in the industry, established trust based relations with leading PVC processors worldwide, and have become a&nbsp;<strong>leading PVC heat stabilizers suppliers and exporters in the world</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>THE PRODUCT - PVC HEAT STABILIZERS</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide PVC Heat Stabilizers (one packs - lead based &amp; calcium-zinc non-toxic) in powder and flakes form. In PVC Processing (extrusion, injection molding, etc.), the polymer is subjected to a high temperature which can lead to burning (degradation or breaking of polymer chains). Heat stabilizers are lead compounds that are added to prevent burning by capturing and inactivating the labile chlorine that is produced on heating of PVC.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Conventionally, a combination of three chemicals, TBLS, DBLS, and LS (Tribasic lead sulphate, dibasic Lead stearate, and Lead stearate) were used as heat stabilizers along with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/calcium-stearate-manufacturers.html\">Calcium Stearate&nbsp;</a>as a co-stabilizer. MLA Group is the leading manufacture of these&nbsp;<strong>single stabilizers</strong>&nbsp;in the highest purity and performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nowadays, one&ndash;pack stabilizer is used in place of the three chemicals as a heat stabilizer. It is made by in-situ reaction of lead oxide with stearic acid along with many other components like waxes, antioxidants, inorganic stabilizers etc, which were not there in the conventional system of single stabilizers above.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Its performance depends on two things:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;the lead oxide content which provides stabilization by deactivating the chloride radical formed during heated melt processing of PVC during extrusion and</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>by providing lubrication so that the residence time inside the screw extruder (heated zone) is reduced, so less deterioration is there.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group produces a dozen of popular one-pack grades with different lead contents as well as over a hundred customized grades.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>WHY CHOOSE US AS YOUR PVC HEAT STABILIZERS SUPPLIERS IN INDIA</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of Industries has been a leading name as&nbsp;<strong>PVC heat stabilizer manufacturers in the world</strong>, known for providing products that are backed by a superior quality guarantee and that conform to international standards. We have a fully-equipped, in-house laboratory with trained and experienced specialists who work with customers to develop products as per specific needs and requirements. Our PVC laboratory has a two roll mixing mill, a Rheometer, moulding press for making sheet, Congo red tester, VR/ IR tester, a pilot extrusion line etc. The application lab helps us in developing value added products and providing technical support to our customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a company that thrives on providing technical support to cater the customer needs. We make sure that our products pass a series of quality control checks before they reach our customers. Our stringent quality checks procedures are inspected regularly in order to maintain