hermal stability and negligible heavy metal contents. For more information, you can contact us, and we will definitely guide you in your selection based on your needs and requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>WHY MLA CALCIUM STEARATE IS GOOD FOR PLASTICS ?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We have a full fledged in-house plastic lab equipped with a two roll mill, moulding press, rheometer, pilot extruder, VR tester, congo red tester, stability ovens etc. to develop high performance products that give excellent gelation and internal lubrication. We have in house Pipe and cable technologists to provide technical support to our customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<h3>CALCIUM STEARATE</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Stearates manufacturing is a simple process but difficult to perfect, as the optimum combination of all properties has to be delicately maintained. MLA Group of Industries is a reputed name among chemical industries and one of the&nbsp;<strong>leading Calcium Stearate manufacturers in India</strong>, with more than 40 years of history in the production of calcium stearate. At MLA Group, we have a complete quality assurance system, accompanied by more than a dozen chemical and technology experts, engineers, and other technical consultants, which have become our company&#39;s strong backing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today, we are one of the largest&nbsp;<strong>Calcium Stearate exporters in India&nbsp;</strong>, catering to every segment of the market with user-specific products. Due to our huge installed capacity of 5000 tons per month, we have the advantage of economies of scale and can offer very competitive prices to our customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>THE PRODUCT - CALCIUM STEARATE</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Calcium stearate, also known as calcium salt and octadecanoic acid, is an odorless white powder used in many manufacturing processes and preparations. It is a carboxylate created by heating stearic acid and calcium oxide under controlled conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group, we manufa