product as per the customer&#39;s formulation need by modifying particular properties to their need.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>WHICH PHARMACOPEIA DOES MLA GROUP FOLLOW?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We manufacture products as per the following</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Indian Pharmacopeia - IP</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;British Pharmacopeia - BP</li>\r\n	<li>US Pharmacopeia - USP</li>\r\n	<li>European Pharmacopeia - EP</li>\r\n	<li>Japanese Pharmacopeia - JP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Apart from this multi-compendia grades are also available which meet all of the above monographs for a particular substance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>HOW CAN I GET THE DOCUMENTS REQUIRED FOR STATUTORY APPROVALS IN MY COMPANY?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA provides Technical Data Pack ( TDP ) to its customers containing all certifications, declarations, COA, TDS, MOA, stability data etc for each substance in a single file. Hence the workload of customer to compile and assimilate information at one place is reduced. Apart from this the Site Master File ( SMF ), Drug Master file ( DMF ) -open part are available for customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>IS MLA OPEN FOR CUSTOMER AUDIT?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, we welcome our customers to audit us as it is a very important step to building trust between the organizations. It also helps us to learn from our customers and improve our processes. We can support both physical and virtual ( on-line audit ).</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4>RANGE OF PRODUCTS</h4>\r\n\r\n<h3>UNISIL</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"UNISIL\" src=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/img/brands/01.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/silica.html\">Precipitated silica</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/download/unisil/Al_Sil_NK_20A_HS_06.pdf\">Sodium Aluminium Silicate</a></li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/silicate.html\">Hydrated Calcium Silicate</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>UNIFLOW</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>UNICELL</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>Micronized Mineral fillers / extenders</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>UNISTAB</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>ZINCOSIL</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>UNILUB</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Being, one of the leading Pharma Excipients exporters in India, we always have been a preferred supplier for Pharma Excipient. We are currently serving more than 43 countries around every corner of the globe. Our constant growth is making us a Leading Pharma Excipients supplier and manufactures in India &amp; in the world At MLA Group, we make items under a controlled climate and with high exactness. Because of our gigantic limit and forceful methodology, our costs are generally practical. We are a main leading Pharma Excipients manufacturers in India who is focused on the quality of our products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All specifications given here are only indicative, there are several application specific grades under each category, please write to us for exact specifications.</p>\r\n', '2024-04-25 08:20:40', '2024-04-25 08:20:40');
