(71, 'Ethylene Bis Stearamide', 'ethylene-bis-stearamide', 'Leading Ethylene Bis Stearamide Exporter & Supplier in India', 'MLA Group is a leading Indian manufacturer & supplier of Ethylene Bis Stearamide, we are one of the best exporters of EBS in the world offering the best price.', 'code', 'product-image/pvc-heat-stabilizer-250x250.webp', '\"59,61,63\"', '16', 'Unpublished', '<h2>ETHYLENE BIS STEARAMIDE (EBS)</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of Industries is a leading Ethylene Bis Stearamide manufacturer in the World. We are a comprehensive enterprise focusing on the development of plastic waxes, stabilizers, and lubricants, integrating scientific research, production, sales, and services. Since the establishment of the company, we have been committed to providing high-quality chemicals, offering a strong guarantee for the advancement of product technology, the stability of quality, and the completeness of after-sales service. We never overcharge our customers and there is no concept of opportunity cost in our company. Hence our prices are always most competitive both in domestic and international markets.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>SYNONYMS</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1,2-Bis(stearoylamino) ethane.</li>\r\n	<li>N,N&#39; - Ethylene bis stearamide</li>\r\n	<li>N,N&#39;-1,2-Ethanediylbisoctadecanamide.</li>\r\n	<li>N,N&#39;-Ethylenedi(stearamide)</li>\r\n	<li>Ethylene distearylamide.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>ETHYLENE BIS STEARAMIDE MANUFACTURERS IN INDIA - OUR PRODUCT</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ethylene Bis Stearamide or EBS by MLA Group has low acid value ( free fatty acid ), high melting point, and excellent white colour, and high purity. Used as a high melting lubricant for engineering plastics, masterbatches, filler compounds, rubber, etc, EBS is compatible with most waxes and plasticizers. The polarity of its two central amide groups and the non-polarity of the two fatty chains make this product an excellent surface-active agent which is incompatible with virtually all solve